commit.message:
i386.h (ADDITIONAL_REGISTER_NAMES): Add sil, dil, bpl and spl aliases.

	* config/i386/i386.h (ADDITIONAL_REGISTER_NAMES): Add
	sil, dil, bpl and spl aliases.

From-SVN: r267456
